## Page Description

Buttons Section

    Extract Themes Button: When clicked, the app extracts themes from the feedback dataset.
    Classify Feedback Button: After themes are extracted, this button classifies the feedback row by row.

Visualizations Section

    Extracted Themes (Bar Chart):
    A bar chart summarizing the number of feedback entries categorized under each theme.

    Classification Results (Pie Chart):
    A pie chart showing the proportion of:
        Classified rows
        Rows marked as "Cannot Classify"

    Sentiment Breakdown (Pie Chart):
    A pie chart visualizing customer sentiment distribution:
        Positive (e.g., Satisfied)
        Neutral
        Negative (e.g., Frustrated)

    Summary Stats:
        Total rows classified.
        Count of rows that couldn't be classified.
        Sentiment proportions.